/F1 8.5 Tf
9.7749999999999986 TL
0.196 g
56.6929133858267775 299.0553543307086102 Td
(A\) Pure scientific experimentation) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 8.5 Tf
9.7749999999999986 TL
0.196 g
297.6377952755905767 299.0553543307086102 Td
(B\) Time and motion studies) Tj
