BT
/F1 8.5 Tf
9.7749999999999986 TL
0.196 g
56.6929133858267775 205.5120472440944468 Td
(A\) From empowering managers to empowering employees) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 8.5 Tf
9.7749999999999986 TL
0.196 g
297.6377952755905767 205.5120472440944468 Td
(B\) From formal controls to peer pressure controls) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 8.5 Tf
9.7749999999999986 TL
0.196 g
56.6929133858267775 192.7561417322833677 Td
(C\) From a trickle-down approach to ad hoc decision making) Tj
