BT
/F1 8.5 Tf
9.7749999999999986 TL
0.196 g
297.6377952755905767 192.7561417322833677 Td
(D\) From specialised job design to generalised job design) Tj
ET
BT
/F2 8 Tf
9.1999999999999993 TL
0.086 0.639 0.29 rg
56.6929133858267775 177.1655905511810261 Td
(Answer: A\) From empowering managers to empowering employees. In modern flatter organisational structures, empowerment has shifted toward the employees) Tj
ET
BT
/F2 9 Tf
10.3499999999999996 TL
0.051 g
56.6929133858267775 145.9844881889763428 Td
