/F1 8.5 Tf
9.7749999999999986 TL
0.196 g
297.6377952755905767 111.9687401574801697 Td
(B\) Eliminating all levels of middle management) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 8.5 Tf
9.7749999999999986 TL
0.196 g
56.6929133858267775 99.2128346456692043 Td
(C\) Improving overall administration from the top level of) Tj
