BT
/F2 8 Tf
9.1999999999999993 TL
0.086 0.639 0.29 rg
56.6929133858267775 83.6222834645668627 Td
(Answer: C\) Improving overall administration from the top level of management. Fayol's administrative theory took a top-down approach to improve managerial efficiency, whereas Taylor took a bottom-up approach focused on workers) Tj
